title: The World of Antiques, Art, and Architecture in Victorian USA
description:
The World of Antiques, Art, and Architecture in Victorian America
E. P. Dutton | 1979 | ISBN: 052512912X | English | 536 pages | PDF | 82 MB


This resource focuses on the American Victorian home. The book is a challenge to navigate because chapter divisions like "Man's World" and "Woman's World." There are 45 color plates supplementing a large amount of black and white photographs
